#

Chickpea and Spinach Stuffed Bell Peppers with Feta Cheese

$12
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

VegetarianHealthyStuffed PeppersComfort Food

Description

A delightful combination of chickpeas and spinach, stuffed in vibrant bell peppers and topped with creamy feta cheese.

Ingredients

  • Bell Peppers: 4 large
  • Chickpeas: 1 can (15 oz), drained and rinsed
  • Fresh Spinach: 2 cups, chopped
  • Feta Cheese: 1 cup, crumbled
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • Cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • Paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Lemon Juice: 1 tablespoon
